    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-04-26T21:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-04-26T21:00:00-05:00" n="750"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d750">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">550.AD1/281b: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Winant</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-04-26T22:00:00-04:00"
                            >April 26, 1943—10 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>2643. Your 2826, April 22.<note n="33" xml:id="d750fn33">Not printed.</note>
                    Murphy has been authorized, on the understanding that a delegation is being
                    named jointly by the High Command and the National Committee, to extend to the
                    appropriate French authorities the formal invitation to the food conference
                    quoted in the Department’s circular telegram of March 24, 9 p.m.<note n="34"
                        xml:id="d750fn34">See footnote 13, <ref target="#pg_825">p.
                        825</ref>.</note> and to assure the French authorities that the French
                    representatives will participate in the conference with the same status as
                    representatives of other countries. Admiral Stark may so inform the French
                    National Committee.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
